snippet.title: Paralegal Reacts to Jennifer Howell's Statement for JOHNNY DEPP
snippet.description:
PARALEGAL REACTS TO JOHNNY DEPP V. AMBER HEARD

So today I reacted to the Statement of Jennifer Howell, made in support of Johnny Depp. Her statement can be found on Adam Waldman twitter account, link is here: https://twitter.com/adam_waldman/status/1291631916844810242

Also gonna link Lost Beyond Pluto, who is a lawyer who breaks down the legality of this case very professionally: https://www.youtube.com/c/lostbeyondpluto

Link to Incredibly Average, he has covered this case in depth from beginning to very recently.. including animated re-enactments etc. Highly recommend!: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg0C-N_MPYYOXyF4T3jMxNQ

Thank you so much for the love on my last videos I really appreciate it! It's really motivating me to keep it up. I hope this was helpful or enjoyable in some way. I plan to keep up with this case so stay tuned and make sure you are subscribed and turn your notification bell on!
